              <h3>Equisys</h3>
              <p class="role-desc">Document and expense software</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="role-right">
            <span>Jun 2010 – Jul 2013</span>
            <span>Office ERP</span>
            <span>London</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <ul>
          <li>Full development lifecycle of ERP software in .NET and C++ for desktop and web applications in a team of 8, reporting to senior leads and CTO</li>
          <li>Integration with Microsoft Office, SharePoint, Dynamics NAV, PDF and fax processing</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="tech-badges">
          <span data-tech="dotnet">.NET</span><span data-tech="cpp">C++</span><span data-tech="microsoft">MS Office</span><span data-tech="dotnet">Dynamics NAV</span><span data-tech="azure">Azure</span>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="role">
        <div class="role-header">
          <div class="role-left">
            <img src="/logos/iminds.png" alt="iMinds" class="role-logo" />
            <div class="role-info">
              <span class="role-title">Research Software Engineer</span>
              <h3>iMinds</h3>
              <p class="role-desc">MobiThin: European research project bringing industry partners together around thin client architecture</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="role-right">
            <span>Oct 2008 – Jun 2010</span>
            <span>Research</span>
            <span>Ghent, Belgium</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <ul>
          <li>Remote desktop protocol and network/bandwidth optimization</li>
          <li>Implementation of network tools for monitoring and load testing in C++</li>
          <li>Test execution scripting in Bash</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="tech-badges">
          <span data-tech="cpp">C++</span><span data-tech="unix">RFB</span><span data-tech="unix">Bash</span><span data-tech="perl">Perl</span><span data-tech="grafana">Zabbix</span>
        </div>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section id="skills">
      <h2>Skills</h2>

      <div class="two-col">
        <div class="col">
          <h3 class="col-title">Hard</h3>

          <div class="skills-section">
            <h4>Languages & Frameworks</h4>
            <p>NodeJS, Python, .NET, PHP, REST, GraphQL, WebSocket, gRPC, React, Angular, Next.js, HTML5</p>
          </div>

          <div class="skills-section">
            <h4>AWS</h4>
            <p>CloudFormation, CloudTrail, CloudWatch, CodeBuild, EC2, ECS, ElastiCache, Lambda, RDS, S3, WAF</p>
          </div>

          <div class="skills-section">
            <h4>Azure</h4>
            <p>AD, App Gateway, Blob Storage, Log Analytics, VMs</p>
          </div>

          <div class="skills-section">
            <h4>Testing</h4>
            <p>K6, Mocha, Jest, NUnit, OpenAPI, Storybook</p>
          </div>

          <div class="skills-section">
            <h4>Databases & Messaging</h4>
            <p>MySQL, PostgreSQL, InfluxDB, Redis, RabbitMQ, Pusher, ServiceBus</p>
          </div>

          <div class="skills-section">
            <h4>DevOps & Infrastructure</h4>
            <p>Docker, K8S, Helm, Jenkins, TeamCity, Octopus</p>
          </div>

          <div class="skills-section">
            <h4>Monitoring</h4>
            <p>ELK, Grafana, NewRelic, Zabbix</p>
          </div>

          <div class="skills-section">
            <h4>Integrations</h4>
            <p>HubSpot, Jitsi, Okta, OneLogin, Office365, Mapbox, Salesforce, Stripe, Zapier, Zendesk</p>
          </div>

          <div class="skills-section">
            <h4>Other</h4>
            <p>LM Studio, LangChain</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col">
          <h3 class="col-title">Soft</h3>

          <div class="skills-section">
            <h4>Data-driven</h4>
            <p>Using data-driven insights to inform strategic and technical decisions</p>
          </div>
          <div class="skills-section">
            <h4>Team scaling</h4>
            <p>Building and nurturing high-performing teams through recruitment, mentorship and career growth</p>
          </div>
          <div class="skills-section">
            <h4>Cloud & Infrastructure</h4>
            <p>Managing multi-cloud infrastructure for scalable, reliable operations</p>
          </div>
          <div class="skills-section">
            <h4>Methodology driven</h4>
            <p>Driving team efficiency and agility by adopting proven methodologies</p>
          </div>
          <div class="skills-section">
            <h4>Strategic direction</h4>
            <p>Leading architectural transformations aligned with strategic business goals</p>
          </div>
          <div class="skills-section">
            <h4>Compliance & security</h4>
            <p>Ensuring robust security and compliance with ISO 27001 and OWASP standards</p>
          </div>
          <div class="skills-section">
            <h4>Continuous Improvement</h4>
            <p>Cultivating a "No blame, No shame" culture of learning and knowledge sharing</p>
          </div>
          <div class="skills-section">
            <h4>Time management</h4>
            <p>Balancing short-term delivery with long-term priorities</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="education">
      <h2>Education</h2>

      <article class="role">
        <div class="role-header">
          <div class="role-left">
            <img src="/logos/uphf.png" alt="UPHF" class="role-logo" />
            <div class="role-info">
              <span class="role-title">Masters Computer Sciences</span>
              <h3>Université Polytechnique Hauts de France</h3>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="role-right">
            <span>2005 – 2008</span>
            <span>Valenciennes, France</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="role">
        <div class="role-header">
          <div class="role-left">
            <img src="/logos/uphf.png" alt="UPHF" class="role-logo" />
            <div class="role-info">
              <span class="role-title">HND Computer Sciences</span>
              <h3>Institut Universitaire de Technologie</h3>
